  <description><![CDATA[<p>Built in the early twentieth century the Grand Hotel Sitea is located on a pedestrianised street in the heart of Risorgimento <a data-udi="umb://document/65aa4a2626424153a1c1c3685d2607aa" href="/{localLink:umb://document/65aa4a2626424153a1c1c3685d2607aa}" title="Turin">Turin,</a> situated just behind the Via Roma and Piazza San Carlo, and minutes away from the portico lined Piazza Castello. Right in the heart of the city, you'll be in the perfect place to wander the streets taking in the attractions, museums and the luxury shopping the city offers. It's also close to Porta Nuova train station, making it easy to explore the surrounding areas during your stay. </p>
<p>The hotel is steeped in family tradition and blends together the classic and the modern, offering comfortable accommodation in a stylish and luxurious setting. The building retains some of its original features such as the coffered ceilings and breakfast room chandelier. </p>
<p>Transfer time: approx. 35 mins by private car</p>]]></description>
